gui.view

Interface IGUI

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    GUIActorImageViewer, GUILevelInspector, GUILibrary, GUIMain, GUIMainScreen

    public interface IGUI
    This interface contains the information that the frontend (of the authoring environment) will pass to the backend (of the authoring environment). The model will call these methods in order to change the data representation of the authoring environment, after receiving input from the user using the environment.
